The '''Thorip Norr''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] located in the [[Lola Curich Starport]], on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Lianna/Legends|Lianna]]. It was owned and operated by the [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Ithmir]] and catered to mostly non-human [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]].<ref name="MtL" />

